snippet.title: CHANEL Fall-Winter 2022/23 Haute Couture Show, The Film of the Show — CHANEL Shows
snippet.description:
Unveiled at the Étrier de Paris equestrian centre, the CHANEL Fall-Winter 2022/23 Haute Couture collection by Virginie Viard was shown within the second chapter of an artistic dialogue with Xavier Veilhan. Graphic silhouettes nuanced with fantasy tweeds and noble embellishments created optical illusions, as Pharrell Williams played the drums on screen to an exclusive track for CHANEL.

See more at https://www.chanel.com/-YT-HC_FW22-23

Setting by Xavier Veilhan.

#CHANELHauteCouture #CHANEL #CHANELShow

snippet.title: CHANEL Fall-Winter 2022/23 Haute Couture Show, Silver Siren — CHANEL Shows
snippet.description:
In a dazzling expression of the Haute Couture savoir-faire, a collarless silver jacket and matching pencil skirt are entirely embroidered with metallic sequins of varying sizes and textures, revealing fractal geometric patterns across a single shimmering surface.

localizations.fr.title: Défilé Haute Couture Automne-Hiver 2022/23 de CHANEL, Sirène d’argent — Défilés CHANEL
localizations.fr.description:
Expression étincelante des savoir-faire de Haute Couture, une veste argentée sans col et une jupe crayon assortie sont entièrement brodées de paillettes irisées de tailles et de textures différentes, révélant des motifs géométriques en fractale sur un même pan resplendissant.

Voir toutes les silhouettes défilé Haute Couture Automne-Hiver 2022/23 sur chanel.com

snippet.title: The Film of the CHANEL Cruise 2022/23 Show — CHANEL Shows
snippet.description:
Held at Monte-Carlo Beach, the CHANEL Cruise 2022/23 show tells a story of coastal elegance on the Riviera. The collection designed by Virginie Viard imagines a spirited ode to Monte-Carlo days and nights filled with cosmopolitan elegance, glamour and speed.

snippet.title: The Film of the Spring-Summer 2022 Haute Couture Show — CHANEL Shows
snippet.description:
The CHANEL Spring-Summer 2022 Haute Couture show, imagined by Virginie Viard, took place at the Grand Palais Éphémère, in a setting designed by Xavier Veilhan. Sébastien Tellier, author-composer and friend of the House, performed a series of new tracks specially composed for the occasion on oversized instruments, and the Cristal Baschet, a rare crystal organ from the Studio Venezia of the French Pavilion at the 57th Venice Biennale in 2017. 

Cristal Baschet © ADAGP Paris 2022

See more at chanel.com

The CHANEL Spring-Summer 2022 Haute Couture show, imagined by Virginie Viard, took place at the Grand Palais Éphémère, in a setting designed by Xavier Veilhan. Sébastien Tellier, author-composer and friend of the House, performed a series of new tracks specially composed for the occasion on oversized instruments, and the Cristal Baschet, a rare crystal organ from the Studio Venezia of the French Pavilion at the 57th Venice Biennale in 2017. 

Cristal Baschet © ADAGP Paris 2022

Le défilé Haute Couture Printemps-Été 2022 de CHANEL, imaginé par Virginie Viard, s’est déroulé au Grand Palais Éphémère, dans une mise en scène conçue par Xavier Veilhan. snippet.title: CHANEL Fall-Winter 2022/23 Haute Couture Show, Haute Couture in Mouvement — CHANEL Shows
snippet.description:
In a dreamlike film by Xavier Veilhan for the Fall-Winter 2022/23 Haute Couture show, CHANEL ambassador Charlotte Casiraghi, Sébastien Tellier, model Vivienne Rohner and the artist himself travel through fantasy landscapes in perpetual motion. From vintage automobiles and monumental instruments to geometric sharks, a series of vignettes reveal poetic elements from Veilhan’s artistic universe where sculpture, music, and dance intertwine with the CHANEL Haute Couture collection created by Virginie Viard. 

The film of the CHANEL Fall-Winter 2022/23 Haute Couture show will be revealed on Tuesday, July 5th from 2pm Paris time.

Original music by Sébastien Tellier.

#CHANELHauteCouture #CHANEL #CHANELShow

snippet.title: Why I Spent $5,800 On A Chanel Bag
snippet.description:
Double-digit prices hikes have reached the fashion industry. Luxury handbag collector Alyssa Lenore, 31, purchased a Chanel classic flap bag in May 2020 for $5,800. Later that month, the price jumped to around $6,300. Similar bags have jumped nearly 63% since 2019, but demand for these items continues. Watch the video to learn what's driving the rise in prices of these luxury handbags, and how it will impact Chanel.

snippet.title: Chanel - SloMo - Spain 🇪🇸 - National Final Performance - Eurovision 2022
snippet.description:
Chanel will represent Spain at the 2022 Eurovision Song Contest in Turin with the song SloMo.

Chanel is a singer, dancer, and occasional actress, born in Cuba and raised in Spain since she was four years old.

If SloMo sounds like an instant dance floor filler, there’s good reason: her songwriting team have worked with the likes of Madonna, Black Eyed Peas, Britney Spears, Ricky Martin, Mariah Carey and Nicki Minaj.

Serving the competition a double-threat of some top-notch choreography and hairography, few could argue that rising star Chanel didn’t do her utmost to bring her song to life on the Benidorm stage in the first semi-final, and delivered a winning performance at the grand final on Saturday night!

Read more about Chanel and Benidorm Fest 2022 here: https://eurovision.tv/story/chanel-wins-benidorm-fest?%2Fstory%2Fchanel-wins-benidorm-fest=

This live performance is from Benidorm Fest, courtesy of our friends at @RTVE. 

#BenidormFest #ElFestivalQueQuieres #Spain #Chanel #Eurovision #TheSoundOfBeauty

snippet.title: Xclusive! CHANEL: THE CLOSEST TO COUTURE YOU'LL EVER BE! By Loic Prigent
snippet.description:
SOUS TITRES DISPONIBLES!  SUBTITLES ARE AVAILABLE!

Filmed in July 2021. This is Chanel couture form winter 2021-2022! A super closer look at the CHANEL Haute Couture by Virginie Viard! The premières d'atelier explains key silhouettes! Julien films some slow-mo details of the fabric to die for! We're on rue Cambon and in the mirrored stairs, totally exclusive access! The inspiration is painter Marie Laurencin! The bride throws the bouquet and some lucky journalist catches it! Take the time to enjoy this! Hope you have fun watching this!


Filmed with Julien Da Costa 
Edited by Pierre Mauger
Produced by Natacha Morice for DERALF
Post by Rafaele Nix Secondi and Konstantin Maslakov

snippet.title: The 2021/22 Métiers d’art Show — CHANEL Shows
snippet.description:
The CHANEL 2021/22 Métiers d’art show by Virginie Viard took place inside 𝘭𝘦19M, the new Parisian building created by CHANEL dedicated to the Fashion Métiers d’art.
The model, musician and CHANEL ambassador Soo Joo Park AKA Ether joined Daniel Lopatin on stage after walking the show to sing the finale song of the artist’s exclusive soundtrack especially composed for the collection.

See all the looks at https://www.chanel.com/-YT-RTW_MDA22

The health and safety of our guests and crews is our priority. A strict sanitary protocol has been implemented during these events.

localizations.fr.title: Le défilé Métiers d’art 2021/22 — Défilés CHANEL
localizations.fr.description:
Le défilé Métiers d’art 2021/22 de CHANEL imaginé par Virginie Viard s’est tenu au cœur du 19M, le nouveau bâtiment créé par CHANEL et dédié aux Métiers d’art de la Mode.
Lors du final, la DJ, mannequin et ambassadrice de CHANEL Soo Joo Park, sous son nom de scène Ether, a rejoint l’artiste Daniel Lopatin sur scène afin d’interpréter un titre spécialement composé par le musicien pour la playlist de la collection.

Voir toutes les silhouettes sur chanel.com

La santé et la sécurité de nos invités et de nos équipes sont notre priorité. Un protocole sanitaire strict a été mis en œuvre lors de ces événements.

snippet.title: 2021/22 Métiers d’art Show in Florence, The CHANEL Masterclass — CHANEL Shows
snippet.description:
In front of an audience of students from Italian fashion, design, art and engineering schools, the 5th edition of the CHANEL Masterclass, held at the Camera di Commercio in Florence, brought together Bruno Pavlovsky, President of CHANEL’s Fashion Activities, actress and ambassador Penélope Cruz, ambassador and spokesperson Caroline de Maigret, and choreographer Dimitri Chamblas. 

Answering questions from Tyler Brûlé and the students, they discussed the dialogue between creation and savoir-faire, the importance of craftsmen and the emotion of creation in a world in constant transformation. 

See more at https://www.chanel.com/-YT-MDA22_FL 

00:00 Introduction by Tyler Brûlé and Bruno Pavlovsky
02:00 Bruno Pavlovsky on the fashion savoir-faire
16:00 Caroline de Maigret and Dimitri Chamblas on the Métiers d’art
33:00 Penélope Cruz on fashion, creation and acting performance
01:01:00 Final thoughts with Bruno Pavlovsky

localizations.fr.title: Défilé Métiers d’art 2021/22 à Florence, La Masterclass de CHANEL — Défilés CHANEL
localizations.fr.description:
Devant un public d'étudiants des écoles italiennes de mode, de design, d'art et d'ingénierie, la 5e édition de la masterclass de CHANEL, organisée à la Camera di Commercio de Florence, réunissait Bruno Pavlovsky, Président des Activités Mode de CHANEL, l'actrice et ambassadrice, Penélope Cruz, l'ambassadrice et porte-parole, Caroline de Maigret, et le chorégraphe Dimitri Chamblas. 
Répondant aux questions de Tyler Brûlé et des étudiants, ils ont échangé sur le dialogue entre création et savoir-faire, l'importance des artisans et l'émotion de la création, dans un monde en constante transformation. 

Voir plus sur https://www.chanel.com/-YT-MDA22_FL

02:00 Bruno Pavlovsky à propos du savoir-faire dans la Mode
16:00 Caroline de Maigret et Dimitri Chamblas à propos des Métiers d’art

snippet.description:
SOUS TITRES FRANCAIS DISPONIBLES!
CHANEL's artistic director VIRGINIE VIARD grants us a stroll on the rooftops of Paris! This is CHANEL Summer 2020 collection! Cardi B and Jennie Kim have flown for the event. Kaia Gerber, Gigi Hadid and Anok Yai and Maike Inga are here to impress. 
I try to learn about all the visual influences of the collection, from Nouvelle Vague film posters, to Anna Karina and pointillist painter George Seurat!

Edited by Konstantin Maslakov! Filmed with Julien Da Costa!

MY LATEST VIDEOS :
HOW TO WALK LIKE A SUPERMODEL?  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p9sTq8vDmH8

CHANEL'S HAUTE COUTURE SECRETS! https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vCOzF0n4-Q4


MORE ME HERE : 
SUBSCRIBE 〉 https://tinyurl.com/y3fcc8ov

INSTAGRAM 〉 https://www.instagram.com/loicprigent/



#CHANEL #김제니 #JENNIEKIM

snippet.title: Literary Rendezvous at Rue Cambon Invite Chantal Thomas — CHANEL Events
snippet.description:
For the sixth edition of the Rendez-vous littéraires rue Cambon [Literary Rendezvous at Rue Cambon], the House of CHANEL along with ambassador and spokesperson for the House Charlotte Casiraghi invites writer Chantal Thomas from the Académie française.

Animated by literary historian Fanny Arama, this encounter begins with the presentation of Chantal Thomas’ work which explores a variety of genres — novels, historical accounts, literary essays or chronicles — followed by the reading of an extract from her last book ‘Journal de nage’ by Anamaria Vartolomei. Together, they evoke the liberation of women's bodies, which is fundamental to the work of Chantal Thomas.

See more at https://www.chanel.com/-YT-Rdvlitteraires22_CT

00:00 Opening by Charlotte Casiraghi
01:46 Presentation of Chantal Thomas by Charlotte Casiraghi
07:31 Extract from ‘Journal de nage’ by Anamaria Vartolomei
10:25 The birth of a writer
12:02 The link between swimming and writing   
15:07 On the liberation of the woman’s body
18:11 Reading of an extract from ‘Souffrir’ by Anamaria Vartolomei
21:31  Chantal Thomas on Madame de Staël
25:36  The spirit of conversation and the literary salons
28:08  Chantal Thomas on Madame du Deffand
30:40  Anamaria Vartolomei on her role in ‘L’échange des princesses’ 
36:29 Extract from “Comment supporter sa liberté” by Anamaria Vartolomei
39:37 Motherhood as a social injunction
40:34 Chantal Thomas on Colette
42:40  Chantal Thomas on the Marquis de Sade
45:18 The role of philosophy in Chantal Thomas’ work
48:03  The role of clothing
48:04 Advice for aspiring writers

#CHANELRendezvousLitteraires #CHANEL

localizations.fr.title: Les Rendez-vous littéraires rue Cambon invitent Chantal Thomas — CHANEL Évènements
localizations.fr.description:
Pour la sixième édition des Rendez-vous littéraires rue Cambon, CHANEL et Charlotte Casiraghi, ambassadrice et porte-parole de la Maison, invitent l’écrivaine Chantal Thomas de l’Académie française.

Animée par l’historienne de la littérature Fanny Arama, cette conversation débute par la présentation de l’œuvre de Chantal Thomas qui explore différents genres — romans, récits historiques, essais littéraires ou chroniques — suivie par la lecture d’un extrait de son dernier ouvrage « Journal de nage » par Anamaria Vartolomei. Ensemble, elles évoquent la libération du corps de la femme, fondamentale dans l’œuvre de Chantal Thomas.

Voir plus sur https://www.chanel.com/-YT-Rdvlitteraires22_CT

For the sixth edition of the Rendez-vous littéraires rue Cambon [Literary Rendezvous at Rue Cambon], the House of CHANEL along with ambassador and spokesperson for the House Charlotte Casiraghi invites writer Chantal Thomas from the Académie française.

Animated by literary historian Fanny Arama, this encounter begins with the presentation of Chantal Thomas’ work which explores a variety of genres — novels, historical accounts, literary essays or chronicles — followed by the reading of an extract from her last book ‘Journal de nage’ by Anamaria Vartolomei. Together, they evoke the liberation of women's bodies, which is fundamental to the work of Chantal Thomas.

See more at https://www.chanel.com/-YT-Rdvlitteraires22_CT
